How'd you meet him?

17
00:02:32,152 --> 00:02:33,825
I was in a car accident
last month.

18
00:02:34,788 --> 00:02:37,928
I won a swimming trophy in high school.
Your turn.

19
00:02:39,593 --> 00:02:41,038
