Obviously,
obviously you had a plan.

67
00:04:50,056 --> 00:04:51,160
The more
interesting question is,

68
00:04:51,258 --> 00:04:52,737
why you didn't tell the team.

69
00:04:52,826 --> 00:04:54,601
I think it's because part
